              scale(time_of_account) +
              scale(voices) + 
              scale(full_time_equivalent_fte_teachers_state_2015_16) +
              
              scale(c_ideology) + 
              scale(g_ideology) + 
              
              scale(pct_students_frpl) +
              scale(teacher_student_ratio) + 
              scale(state_spending_per_child) + 
              
              (1|state),
